Class CreateServiceKeyRequest.Builder

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cloudfoundry.operations.services.CreateServiceKeyRequest.Builder
  • Enclosing class:
    CreateServiceKeyRequest

    public static final class CreateServiceKeyRequest.Builder
extends Object
    Builds instances of type CreateServiceKeyRequest. Initialize attributes and then invoke the build() method to create an immutable instance.

    Builder is not thread-safe and generally should not be stored in a field or collection, but instead used immediately to create instances.
